00:23:05.620 --> 00:23:06.380
 Father!

00:23:06.380 --> 00:23:07.620
 Oh, just a minute, Alice.

00:23:07.620 --> 00:23:09.180
 Father, guess who was at the door?

00:23:09.180 --> 00:23:09.660
 Who?

