 Every Saturday.

00:23:25.660 --> 00:23:27.260
 Sam, it's midnight.

00:23:27.260 --> 00:23:27.860
 But...

00:23:27.860 --> 00:23:29.460
 Happy New Year, Sam.

00:23:29.460 --> 00:23:31.460
 Happy New Year, Father.

00:23:31.460 --> 00:23:32.460
 Yes.

00:23:32.460 --> 00:23:33.860
 Well...

